				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\kappa n_{D_{\ell }}, \ell =1,\dots,L$\end{document}κnDℓ,ℓ=1,…,L DE genes with a pattern of differential gene expression observed in the DE gene subset D
ℓ, respectively.
